dejv.commons.jfx.geometry

Class ObservableBounds

  • java.lang.Object
    • dejv.commons.jfx.geometry.ObservableBounds
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CompositeObservableBounds

    public class ObservableBounds
extends Object
    Replacement to Bounds with observable coords.

    The class offers following properties to observe:

    • minX
    • minY
    • minZ
    • centerX
    • centerY
    • centerZ
    • maxX
    • maxY
    • maxZ
    • width
    • height
    • depth
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    dejv78 (dejv78.github.io)
